	   <tr><td colspan=2>I saw that they changed them to 10 slots and jumped all over them. I now have about 6 in my bank as well as 1 in my guild bank in case anyone in my guild would need to use it. I am on Brell serilis and if anyone would like one of my deluxe sewing kits they could give me a bizuzz. I currently carry around all 10 slots and 1 sewing kit. I am working on tailoring and I like having one incase I need to loot a giant Item. Thanks Verant for letting me have a bunch of 10 slots in my bank for about 1pp each hehe<br><br>Crackercrumbs Buetterscratch<br>Willyj<br>Verakat<br>&nbsp;<br>Crackercrumbs<br>Cute little fart ain't I?</td></tr>
